snippet.title: Emma's Campervan Build: Ep. 4 - Electrics, Diesel Heater & Ceiling
snippet.description:
The first 1,000 people to use this link will get a 1 month free trial of Skillshare: https://skl.sh/projectamber06211

This time we tackle the van's ceiling, using tongue and groove slats, fitting lights, wiring and skylight finishings as we go.
I make a start on the base electrical system so that Emma has lights and power in the van.
We also get the diesel heater in and make some tweaks here there and everywhere.
